# Write Artifacts to Disk

| Output | Location |
| :--- | :--- |
| Execution plan | `docs/plans/active/{name}.md` |
| Spec | `specs/{system}.md` (+ index in `specs/README.md`) |
| Analysis / audit | `docs/reports/{name}.md` |
| Quality / architecture updates | `docs/quality.md`, `docs/architecture.md` |
